// Send Message Workflow
When: "Send" button is clicked
Data:
- Input field: message_content

Steps:
1. Create a new thing:
   - Type: Message
   - Sender: Current User
   - Receiver: Selected User (if private chat)
   - Content: message_content
   - Timestamp: Current Date/Time
   - Is_Group_Chat: yes/no based on chat type

2. Reset Input:
   - Clear message_content field